entor-element elementor-element-3fb9b3c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Cancer-Related Cachexia<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c991400 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c991400\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b748f33\" data-id=\"b748f33\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e878a96 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e878a96\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Cachexia Definition<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Modern Definition<\/em>: A Complex Metabolic Syndrome Associated with Underlying Illness &amp; Characterized by Loss of Muscle with or without Loss of Fat Mass<\/li><li><em>Historical Definition<\/em>: Unintentional Weight Loss &gt; 10% of Body Weight<ul><li>May Underestimate Frequency in Obese Patients<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Most Common Associated Malignancies:<ul><li><strong>Upper GI Malignancy<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Pancreatic Cancer<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Associated with Poor Prognosis &amp; Worse Outcomes<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Presentation<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Weight Loss \u2013 The Prominent Clinical Feature<ul><li>Growth Failure in Pediatrics<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Progressive Muscle Wasting<\/li><li>Sarcopenia \u2013 Loss of Lean Body Mass<\/li><li>Anorexia<\/li><li>Fatigue<\/li><li>Systemic Inflammatory Response<\/li><li>Anemia or Hypoalbuminemia<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Mechanism<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Increased Basal Metabolic Rate &amp; Reduced Dietary Intake<\/li><li>Associated with Proinflammatory Cytokines:<ul><li><strong>TNF-\u03b1<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>IL-1<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>IL-6<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Dietary Counseling<\/li><li>Appetite Stimulants:<ul><li><strong>Progesterone Analogs:<\/strong><ul><li><strong>Megestrol Acetate (Megace)<\/strong><\/li><li>Medroxyprogesterone Acetate<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Dexamethasone (Steroid) \u2013 Generally Only Considered for Patients with Short Anticipate Life Expectancy (Days-Weeks)<\/li><li>*Palliative with No Survival Benefit<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Other Pharmacologic Considerations (Inconclusive Benefit):<ul><li>Olanzapine<\/li><li>Mirtazapine<\/li><li>Androgens<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>No High-Quality Evidence to the Efficacy of Inhaled Marijuana or Ingested CBD Oil \u2013 Generally Recommended Against<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fluids, Electrolytes &#038; Nutrition: Cancer-Related Cachexia Cancer-Related Cachexia Cachexia Definition Modern Definition: A Complex Metabolic Syndrome Associated with Underlying Illness &amp; Characterized by Loss of Muscle with or without Loss of Fat Mass Historical Definition: Unintentional Weight Loss &gt; 10% of Body Weight May Underestimate Frequency in Obese Patients Most Common Associated Malignancies: Upper GI [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"folder":[35],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2099"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2099"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2099\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5507,"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2099\/revisions\/5507"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2099"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"folder","embe